    dc:description "Figure 34. Homothermon paulista Ohaus (valid name H. praemorsus Burmeister) type male (see \" Type specimens and lectotype designation \" in Methods) from ZMHB. A Dorsal habitus B Lateral habitus C Specimens labels, mouthparts, and male genitalia D Male genitalia, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/130462" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.666.9191.figure35>
